  title: "TJX Companies (TJX) Intrinsic Value: A DCF Analysis",
  description: "We ran a full discounted cash flow on TJX using FY2026 actuals. One number. Every assumption disclosed. Here's what TJX is really worth.",
  category: "study",
  published: "2026-03-18",
